pageContext.claim: “You know, Maggie Haberman, all of these people. They... I have nothing against them, but they don't know me. They don't know me. I haven't seen her, I haven't spoken to her in a year and a half.”
pageContext.analysis: Haberman was visibly seen traveling often with the president on Air Force One in the preceding 18 months -- and Trump often came to the back of the plane to speak with reporters.
